Module openj9.dtfj
Package com.ibm.j9ddr.corereaders.memory

Interface IAddressSpace

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IMemory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ASNoProcess, BufferedMemory, LinuxProcessAddressSpace, OSXProcessAddressSpace, ProcessAddressSpace, WindowsProcessAddressSpace
    public interface IAddressSpace
extends IMemory
    A region of addressable memory that has an ID and a list of processes. The multiple processes per address space is required to model enclaves on zOS. Most other platforms have one process per A/S.
